s-klausomiausi-2020w13/|title=2020 13-os savait\u0117s klausomiausi (TOP 100)|publisher=[[AGATA (organization)|AGATA]]|language=Lithuanian|url-status=live|accessdate=6 April 2020}}</ref>\n| 17\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Malaysia ([[Recording Industry Association of Malaysia|RIM]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/RecordingIndustryMalaysia/photos/pcb.3357908454236501/3357908324236514/?type=3&theater|title=Top 20 Most Streamed International & Domestic Singles In Malaysia|work=[[Recording Industry Association of Malaysia]]|publisher=Recording Industry Association of Malaysia|accessdate=5 April 2020}}</ref>\n| 7\n|-\n{{single chart|Dutch40|19|year=2020|week=14|rowheader=true|accessdate=4 April 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Dutch100|14|artist=Benee feat. Gus Dapperton|song=Supalonely|rowheader=true|accessdate=4 April 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| New Zealand ([[Recorded Music NZ]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/singles?chart=4838|title=NZ Top 40 Singles Chart|publisher=[[Recorded Music NZ]]|date=28 March 2020|accessdate=28 March 2020}}</ref>\n| 2\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Norway ([[VG-lista]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vglista.no/topplister/topp-20-single-2020-12/|title=VG-lista \u2013 Topp 20 Single uke 12, 2020|publisher=[[VG-lista]]|accessdate=21 March 2020}}</ref>\n| 6\n|-\n{{single chart|Poland|73|chartid=3362|year=2020|rowheader=true|accessdate=6 April 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Portugal|80|artist=Benee feat. Gus Dapperton|song=Supalonely|rowheader=true|accessdate=29 March 2020}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Scotland|51|date=20200403|rowheader=true|accessdate=4 April 2020}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Singapore ([[Recording Industry Association (Singapore)|RIAS]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rias.org.sg/rias-top-charts/|title=RIAS International Top Charts Week 13|publisher=Recording Industry Association (Singapore)|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200403095609/https://www.rias.org.sg/rias-top-charts/|archive-date=3 April 2020}}</ref>\n| 8\n|-\n{{sin