Campbell]] \u2013 arranger, conductor (track 2)\n*[[Ramesh Mishra]] \u2013 [[sarangi]]\n*[[John Webster (musician)|John Webster]] \u2013 keyboards, backing vocals\n*Suzie Katayama - strings, conductor\n\n'''Production'''\n*Producers{{snd}}[[Kevin Shirley]] and Aerosmith\n*Engineers{{snd}}[[Mark Hudson (musician)|Mark Hudson]], Joe Perry, Rory Romano, [[Elliot Scheiner]], Kevin Shirley, Steven Tyler\n*Second engineer{{snd}}Rory Romano\n*Mixing{{snd}}Elliot Scheiner, Kevin Shirley\n*Mastering{{snd}}[[Leon Zervos]]\n*Programming{{snd}}Sander Selover\n*Horn arrangements{{snd}}David Campbell, Steven Tyler\n*String arrangements{{snd}}David Campbell\n*Guitar technicians{{snd}}Jim Survis\n*Guitar technicians (Additional){{snd}}Lisa Sharken, Archie Avila\n*Drum technician{{snd}}Andy Gilman\n*Production engineer{{snd}}David Frangioni\n*Art direction{{snd}}Christopher Austopchuk, Gail Marowitz\n*Photo art direction{{snd}}Christopher Austopchuk, Gail Marowitz\n*Photography{{snd}}F. Scott Schafer\n*Calligraphy{{snd}}Jeanne Greco\n*Stylist{{snd}}Fiona Williams-Chappel\n\nCredits verified from the album's liner notes.<ref name=NL>{{Cite AV media notes |title=Nine Lives |others=Aerosmith |type=liner notes |year=1997 |publisher=[[Columbia Records|Columbia]] |id=CK 67994}}</ref>\n\n==Charts==\n'''Album'''\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n!scope=\"col\"|Chart (1997)\n!scope=\"col\"|Peak<br />position\n|-\n|Australian Top 50 Albums<ref>{{cite web |url=http://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Aerosmith&titel=Nine+Lives&cat=a |title=Aerosmith \u2013 ''Nine Lives'' (Album) |work=[[ARIA Charts|Australian Charts]] |publisher=Hung Medien |format=ASP |accessdate=June 28, 2011}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|13\n|-\n|Austrian Top 75 Albums<ref>{{cite web |url=http://austriancharts.at/showitem.asp?interpret=Aerosmith&titel=Nine+Lives&cat=a |title=Aerosmith \u2013 ''Nine Lives'' (Album) |work=Austrian Charts |publisher=Hung Medien |format=ASP |accessdate=June 28, 2011}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|2\n|-\n|Flanders, Belgium 100 Albums<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ultratop.be/nl/showitem.asp?interpret=Aerosmith&titel=Nine+Lives&cat=a |title=Aerosmith \u2013 ''Nine Lives'' (Album) |work=[[Ultratop]] |publisher=Hung Medien |format=ASP |accessdate=June 28, 2011}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|11\n|-\n|Wallonia, Belgium 100 Albums<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ultratop.be/fr/showitem.asp?interpret=Aerosmith&titel=Nine+Lives&cat=a |title=Aerosmith \u2013 ''Nine Lives'' (Album) |work=[[Ultratop]] |publisher=Hung Medien |format=ASP |accessdate=June 28, 2011}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|5\n|-\n|[[Canadian Albums Chart]]<ref name=\"Billboard\">{{cite web |url={{BillboardURLbyName|artist=aerosmith|chart=all}} |title=''Nine Lives'' by Aerosmith |work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]] |publisher=[[Prometheus Global Media]] |accessdate=June 28, 2011}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|2\n|-\n|Finnish Top 50 Albums<ref>{{cite web |url=http://finnishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Aerosmith&titel=Nine+Lives&cat=a |title=Aerosmith \u2013 ''Nine Lives'' (Album) |work=Finnish Charts |publisher=Hung Medien |format=ASP |accessdate=June 28, 2011}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|1\n|-\n|French Top 100 Albums<ref>{{cite web |url=http://lescharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Aerosmith&titel=Nine+Lives&cat=a |title=Aerosmith \u2013 ''Nine Lives'' (Album) |work=[[Syndicat National de l'\u00c9dition Phonographique|Les Charts]] |publisher=Hung Medien |format=ASP |accessdate=June 28, 2011}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|5\n|-\n|German Albums<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.musicline.de/de/chartverfolgung_summary/artist/AEROSMITH/?type=longplay |title=Chartverfolgung / AEROSMITH / Longplay |work=Music Line |publisher=[[Media Control Charts]] |language=German |accessdate=June 28, 2011 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121017140551/http://www.musicline.de/de/chartverfolgung_summary/artist/AEROSMITH/?type=longplay |archive-date=October 17, 2012 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|3\n|-\n|[[Oricon|Japanese Albums Chart]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oricon.co.jp/prof/artist/46082/ranking/cd_album/|title=\u30a8\u30a2\u30ed\u30b9\u30df\u30b9\u306eCD\u30a2\u30eb\u30d0\u30e0\u30e9\u30f3\u30ad\u30f3\u30b0\u3001\u30a8\u30a2\u30ed\u30b9\u30df\u30b9\u306e\u30d7\u30ed\u30d5\u30a3\u30fc\u30eb\u306a\u3089\u30aa\u30ea\u30b3\u30f3\u82b8\u80fd\u4eba\u4e8b\u5178-ORICON STYLE |publisher=Oricon.co.jp |accessdate=2013-05-02}}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|3\n|-\n|Netherlands Top 100 Albums<ref>{{cite web |url=http://dutchcharts.nl/showitem.asp?interpret=Aerosmith&titel=Nine+Lives&cat=a |title=Aerosmith \u2013 ''Nine Lives'' (Album) |work=Dutch Charts |publisher=Hung Medien |format=ASP |accessdate=June 28, 2011}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|17\n|-\n|New Zealand Top 40 Albums<ref>{{cite web |url=https://charts.nz/showitem.asp?interpret=Aerosmith&titel=Nine+Lives&cat=a |title=Aerosmith \u2013 ''Nine Lives'' (Album) |work=[[Recording Industry Association of New Zealand|New Zealand Charts]] |publisher=Hung Medien |format=ASP |accessdate=June 28, 2011}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|14\n|-\n|Norwegian Top 40 Albums<ref>{{cite web |url=http://norwegiancharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Aerosmith&titel=Nine+Lives&cat=a |title=Aerosmith \u2013 ''Nine Lives'' (Album) |work=[[VG-lista|Norwegian Charts]] |publisher=Hung Medien |format=ASP |accessdate=June 28, 2011}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|6\n|-\n|Spain ([[Productores de M\u00fasica de Espa\u00f1a|AFYVE]])<ref>{{cite book|title=S\u00f3lo \u00e9xitos: a\u00f1o a a\u00f1o, 1959\u20132002|last=Salaverri|first=Fernando|date=September 2005|publisher=Fundaci\u00f3n Autor-SGAE|isbn=84-8048-639-2|edition=1st|location=Spain}}<!--|accessdate=2011-01-26--></ref>\n|align=\"center\"|5\n|-\n|Swedish Top 60 Albums<ref>{{cite web |url=http://swedishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Aerosmith&titel=Nine+Lives&cat=a 