 length14        = 8:18\n| title15         = [[I Don't Want to Miss a Thing]]\n| writer15        = [[Diane Warren]]\n| length15        = 4:56\n}}\n\n==Personnel==\n'''Aerosmith'''\n* [[Steven Tyler]] \u2013 lead vocals, keyboards, [[Barrel organ|hand organ]], piano, harmonica, [[Hammered dulcimer|hammer dulcimer]], percussion\n* [[Joe Perry (musician)|Joe Perry]] \u2013 guitar, [[slide guitar]], [[dulcimer]], backing vocals\n* [[Brad Whitford]] \u2013 guitar, acoustic guitar\n* [[Tom Hamilton (musician)|Tom Hamilton]] \u2013 bass guitar, [[Chapman Stick]]\n* [[Joey Kramer]] \u2013 drums\n\n'''Additional personnel'''\n*[[David Campbell (composer)|David Campbell]] \u2013 arranger, conductor (track 2)\n*[[Ramesh Mishra]] \u2013 [[sarangi]]\n*[[John Webster (musician)|John Webster]] \u2013 keyboards, backing vocals\n*Suzie Katayama - strings, conductor\n\n'''Production'''\n*Producers{{snd}}[[Kevin Shirley]] and Aerosmith\n*Engineers{{snd}}[[Mark Hudson (musician)|Mark Hudson]], Joe Perry, Rory Romano, [[Elliot Scheiner]], Kevin Shirley, Steven Tyler\n*Second engineer{{snd}}Rory Romano\n*Mixing{{snd}}Elliot Scheiner, Kevin Shirley\n*Mastering{{snd}}[[Leon Zervos]]\n*Programming{{snd}}Sander Selover\n*Horn arrangements{{snd}}David Campbell, Steven Tyler\n*String arrangements{{snd}}David Campbell\n*Guitar technicians{{snd}}Jim Survis\n*Guitar technicians (Additional){{snd}}Lisa Sharken, Archie Avila\n*Drum technician{{snd}}Andy Gilman\n*Production engineer{{snd}}David Frangioni\n*Art direction{{snd}}Christopher Austopchuk, Gail Marowitz\n*Photo art direction{{snd}}Christopher Austopchuk, Gail Marowitz\n*Photography{{snd}}F. Scott Schafer\n*Calligraphy{{snd}}Jeanne Greco\n*Stylist{{snd}}Fiona Williams-Chappel\n\nCredits verified from the album's liner notes.<ref name=NL>{{Cite AV media notes |title=Nine Lives |others=Aerosmith |type=liner notes |year=1997 |publisher=[[Columbia Records|Columbia]] |id=CK 67994}}</ref>\n\n==Charts==\n'''Album'''\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\